    {
      "id": "1474833714562203811",
      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2026-02-21T18:22:38.637+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "Hey all, \nI've got a number of components on order so we'll see how things go when I get them. \nA few small changes, I think the chandelier will be direct driven, I have a motor on the way. \n\nI made the first rev chandelier carousel thing. There's quite a lot of things I don't like, but overall I'm liking the direction. \nI have made some changes to the feeders as there wasn't room for the toolhead with the cover tape where it was, so moved it back futher. \nProbably a lot more, but that's what I have in my mind at the moment.",
